dct_title_s: Road map of the State of New Jersey
dct_description_sm: from original surveys of the N.J. Geological Survey ; based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey.
Panel title on verso: Louisiana Purchase Exposition. Map showing the improved wagon roads of New Jersey Macadamized under the State Aid Law.
